name: Cat Content
description:
Cat Content is an Internet phenomenon predominantly belonging to the field of popular culture. The term is a bogus anglicism. In the English-speaking world, on the other hand, the term "cat content" is not widespread. There one speaks of "Cats on the internet".
Cat content refers to the numerous pictures and other representations of cats on the Internet. Cats are generally considered to play a major role in the public sphere. They are considered to be particularly widespread on the worldwide web. In the present, cat content is of particular importance on social media platforms.
